Homing Missile Pod Zoomy
Replaces Mongol

Infinite ammo
Slow reload
Horrible accuracy (But who needs accuracy when you're firing homing missiles)
High firerate
No self damage
Slow projectiles
Big blast radius
10 Round magazine
+2000% Shield capasity
+5000% Shield recharge delay
+2000% Shield regeneration rate
Grants Zoomy Zommy Zoom Zoom speed
Fires upwards and homes towards enemies
Infinite home range (Can home to and hit targets accross the map)

How to use: Just aim at the general direction, and OPEN FIRE!

